{"word":"G5282 - ὑπονοέω - hyponoéō - hoop-on-o-eh'-o - Think","slug":"G5282","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπονοέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>hyponoéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hoop-on-o-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Think"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C5;&#x0314;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - huponoeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>hoop-on-o-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G3539\">G3539</a>; to <i>think under</i> (<i>privately</i>), that is, to <i>surmise</i> or <i>conjecture:</i> - think, suppose, deem."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1270\">G1270</a>, <a href=\"#/G1271\">G1271</a>, <a href=\"#/G1425\">G1425</a>, <a href=\"#/G1771\">G1771</a>, <a href=\"#/G2132\">G2132</a>, <a href=\"#/G2133\">G2133</a>, <a href=\"#/G2657\">G2657</a>, <a href=\"#/G279\">G279</a>, <a href=\"#/G3340\">G3340</a>, <a href=\"#/G3539\">G3539</a>, <a href=\"#/G3540\">G3540</a>, <a href=\"#/G3559\">G3559</a>, <a href=\"#/G3563\">G3563</a>, <a href=\"#/G4306\">G4306</a>, <a href=\"#/G4307\">G4307</a>, <a href=\"#/G453\">G453</a>, <a href=\"#/G454\">G454</a>, <a href=\"#/G5283\">G5283</a>"}]}